{"tid":1892020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"初步確診96歲老婦　與另一確診者曾到北角「福慧精舍」佛堂","createTime":"2020-02-22T09:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T12:43:13.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9bdcbfbc85a5ee3cdaa76a792ad14f0c8dfabc11","tid":1892020,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續，衛生署衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今午（22日）於記者會表示，本港今日無新增確診個案，但有一宗初步確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n初步確診：<br />\n<br />\n．96歲老婦，有心臟長期病患<br />\n<br />\n．居於天后廟道飛龍台，與兒子、媳婦及孫女同住，3人被列為緊密接觸者<br />\n<br />\n．2月3日出現發燒及咳嗽病徵，因腳痛2月初起無出門，無外遊紀錄<br />\n<br />\n．今日凌晨情況轉差有氣促，入住東區醫院<br />\n<br />\n．1月尾曾去過北角美輪大廈13樓E座「福慧精舍」佛堂<br />\n<br />\n．第65宗確診者曾於1月25日、2月1日及2月8日到過該佛堂，去佛堂的人普遍留在佛堂數小時誦經。張竹君呼籲曾到過該佛堂的人聯絡衛生防護中心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200222/s00001/1582358385318/【武漢肺炎】初步確診96歲老婦-與另一確診者曾到北角「福慧精舍」佛堂\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200222%2Fs00001%2F1582358385318%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA96%E6%AD%B2%E8%80%81%E5%A9%A6-%E8%88%87%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%8F%E6%85%A7%E7%B2%BE%E8%88%8D%E3%80%8D%E4%BD%9B%E5%A0%82&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdguNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=572b7124\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200222%2Fs00001%2F1582358385318%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA96%E6%AD%B2%E8%80%81%E5%A9%A6-%E8%88%87%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%8F%E6%85%A7%E7%B2%BE%E8%88%8D%E3%80%8D%E4%BD%9B%E5%A0%82&h=324622ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200222/s00001/1582358385318/【武漢肺炎】初步確診96歲老婦-與另一確診者曾到北角「福慧精舍」佛堂</a>"},{"pid":"91ad1743ede86378924f759afe50b9fb68d84365","tid":1892020,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018a7ee2345c4b72e0dc2c8f052742e83ca32753","tid":1892020,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:16:14.000Z","msg":"唉，我阿公好鍾意去北角佛堂拜我太嫲，唔知有冇去呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042d3ae908add193ca44eb77ce8795754f0e4b46","tid":1892020,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:43:13.000Z","msg":"佛堂d人好藍，信警察多過信佛祖<br />\n<br />\n有親戚番開佛堂"}]}